Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.manager

Class RegistrationManager

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.manager.RegistrationManager
public class RegistrationManager extends Object
This class controls the user that can interact with the Course Catalog or Student Directory. The user can either be a Registrar, who is a university official that maintains the directory of enrolled students, or a Student, who is registered in the system by the Registrar and can create a schedule of courses from courses listed in the Course Catalog that do not conflict with each other.
Author:
Thien Nguyen
